title: Jeff Rosenstock
itunes:title: Jeff Rosenstock
description:
An absolute renaissance man, Jeff Rosenstock, is on the show today to celebrate Thanksgiving with us. Well, not really but we do talk about punk ethics, ska and his youth spent in Long Island, NY. It’s an uplifting chat and I am glad you are “tuning in”. Please have a safe holiday and don’t eat turkey! Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
